annotations.caption: Inside a factory, a man walks while whistling and holding an iron bar, as another man approaches from afar with a flashlight.

A woman in a hat and black dress skateboards outside. She jumps onto the skateboard but falls to the ground. The scene shifts, and the woman successfully lands on the skateboard after another jump, letting out a whiny sound.
Fingers continuously move across the piano keys, producing a harmonious and soothing melody from the instrument.
A vibrant background filled with waves and musical notes gradually fades into darkness, accompanied by a whistling sound.
A big white wind indicator spun in the breeze, with leaves rustling around it.
